invalid type: string "Scheme Name: Kisan Credit Card (KCC)\nCategory: Agriculture\nMinistry: Ministry of Agriculture and Farmers Welfare\nDescription: Provides short-term credit to farmers for agricultural needs at subsidized interest rates.\n\nEligibility: \n    - Farmers (owner cultivators, tenant farmers, sharecroppers, oral lessees)\n    - Self Help Groups and Joint Liability Groups of farmers